fe-threatening ventricular arrhythmias who are incompletely responsive to a single agent or to amiodarone alone.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/21761/', '', 'Amiodarone, Moricizine, Bretylium, Tocainide', 'Quinidine, Tocainide, Moricizine, Bretylium', 1767369485);
